name: Preston Holloway
text: Ah-mazing. I used to ride here all the time. There are some trails further down. Nothing blows the skirt up like racing along the tracks at 70mph and passing a train going the opposite direction at 40mph.

name: Doom Sucker
text: Great part of Andalusias history. I’m the person who added it to the maps so I was so excited to see that it was approved. Now people can get to it a lot easier.
